snippet.title: NZ vs PAK 4th T20I - Cricket Highlights | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Daryl Mitchell and Glenn Phillips dazzled in the 4th T20I, helping NZ win the series  4-0 against Pakistan.

Watch Now - https://bit.ly/NewZealandvsPakistan4thT20I

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: Bigg Boss Triumph : @ElvishYadavVlogs's Comic Chronicles!
snippet.description:
Step into the captivating world of a true entertainer, Elvish Yadav – a well-known Indian Youtuber and winner of Bigg Boss OTT Season 2 . This podcast is your express ticket to Elvish's journey, from his YouTube adventures to the thrill of winning Bigg Boss OTT, all while cherishing the unique connection with his supportive fanbase. It's a brief yet lively chat, giving you a glimpse into the life of a vibrant personality, filled with stories, achievements, and the warmth of a dedicated community. Tune in for a dose of entertainment and insights into the dynamic world of Elvish Yadav!

snippet.title: Weather Update: दिल्ली से लेकर उत्तर भारत तक ठंड का सितम | जानें कैसा रहेगा मौसम | IMD | Hindi News
snippet.description:
Weather Update News: एक तरफ भीषण ठंड तो दूसरी तरफ घने कोहरा का तांडव। देश में सर्दी के तेवर बेहद तीखे बने हैं। ठंड से तो लोग पहले से ही परेशान थे अब कोहरे ने लोगों की परेशानी और बढ़ा दी है। न्यूनतम तापमान में लगातार गिरावट दर्ज की जा रही है। राजधानी दिल्ली में आज सुबह ठंड से कुछ राहत मिली। आज सुबह यहां का तापमान 7.1 डिग्री सेल्सियस दर्ज किया गया, जो सामान्य तापमान से एक डिग्री कम है। हालांकि दिल्ली-एनसीआर में तापमान में बढ़ोतरी के बाद भी ठिठुरन से लोगों को राहत नहीं मिली है। सुबह 4 बजे दिल्ली के IGI एयरपोर्ट पर विजिबिलिटी शून्य मापी गई जिसमें धीरे-धीरे सुधार हुआ लेकिन इसके चलते कई उड़ानें प्रभावित हुईं। 

#weather #weatherreport #weathernews #weatherupdate #weatherforecast #weatherupdatetoday #upweather #weatherupdates #delhiweather #delhincrweather #hindinews #topnews #latestupdates

snippet.title: 100 Million - DIVINE, Karan Aujla | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/100M

'100 Million' is an ode to the unparalleled success achieved by DIVINE and Karan Aujla. This track not only celebrates their achievements but also stands as an anthem, for those with grand dreams. As they savour the fruits of their labour, the artists reflect on the enduring habits that propelled them to the pinnacle. Fueled by explosive bars and bravado, this track marks the inception of a collaborative project between the two industry titans.

 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Reyansh and Aradhna conduct their investigation into the illegal medicine business. Aradhna's mother gets into an accident, and Reyansh takes him to the hospital. Meanwhile, Aradhna tries to call Jai to the hospital, but he is too drunk to pick up her call. What will Aradhna do now?

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: Matka Opening Bracket | Varun tej | Karuna Kumar | Meenakshi | Nora Fatehi | GV Prakash |
snippet.description:
Watch MATKA Opening bracket here! 

#Matka is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun Tej in the Lead Role. Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments.

The story which takes place between 1958-1982, is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas. 

Technical Crew:
Story, Screenplay, Dialogues, Direction: Karuna Kumar
Producers: Dr Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri 
Banners: Vyra Entertainments, SRT Entertainments 
Music: GV Prakash Kumar
DOP: A Kishor Kumar
Editor: Karthika Srinivas R
Production Design: Ashish Teja Pulala
Costumes: Rekha Boggarapu
Executive Producer : EVV Satish, Vidya Sagar J, RK Jana
Line Producer: Prashanth Mandava
DI: Sri Sarathi Studios
PRO: Vamsi Shekar

snippet.title: VEG THALI | 15 Varieties of Veg Recipes | Huge South Indian Veg Thali Recipes Cooking In Village
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 15 varieties of vegetarian recipes for the special Tamil day of the Pongal festival. We cook South Indian Veg thali recipes by cooking the following recipes: Rice, Sambar, Rasam, Mor, Payasam, Appalam, Vadai, Sweet Pongal, Potato fry, Lady Finger masala, Brinjal Masial, Raw banana Fry, Cabbage, Thandu Keerai Masiyal, and Pickle.

The taste is savory!

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Exclusive Look Of The Newly Built Ram Mandir & Ayodhya Airport | I Love My India | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Curly Tales has exclusive access to the newly built Ram Mandir &  Maharishi Valmiki Airport just before the launch. 
The Ram Mandir, set to be inaugurated on January 22nd, has preparations going on in full swing as around 4000 laborers are working on it around the clock. 
The temple is a testament to architectural marvel, constructed without the use of metal or concrete. Instead, a special rock imported from the Bansi Mountain in Rajasthan has been employed.
Along with that get a glimpse of Ayodhya’s four transformed lanes which are the - Bhaktipath, Janma Bhoomi Path, Ram Path & Dharma Path which are reconstructed on the basis of 4 vedas. 
You will also be amazed to see a new systematic way of Darshan for better crowd management that has been arranged by the government. 
Additionally, we give you an exclusive look at the Maharishi Valmiki International Airport, set to launch soon after being constructed in a record time of just 20 months. Inspired by the new Ram Mandir, the airport's walls are adorned with paintings depicting stories from the Ramayana. With the capacity to host about 10 lakh passengers annually, this airport is a remarkable addition to Ayodhya's infrastructure. 
So what are you waiting for,  book your tickets now as various modes of transportation have now been made available to visit Ram Lala.    

#ayodhya #rammandirayodhya #curlytales #foodandtravel #ayodhyadham #ayodhyarammandir #ayodhyatemple #rammandir

snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Telugu

Presenting the first single "Choodu Nanna" from 'Yatra 2' starring Mammootty, Jiiva & others. Directed by Mahi V Raghav, Music Composed by Santhosh Narayanan.

Song Credits:-
Lyrics : Bhaskarabhatla Ravi Kumar
Singers : Vijaynarain
Composed, Arranged and Programmed by Santhosh Narayanan
Additional Vocals : Santhosh Narayanan
Recorded by Santhosh Narayanan, Rupendar Venkatesh
Recorded at Future Tense Studios -  Chennai
Recording Engineer : Rupendar Venkatesh
Studio Assist : Jaba Raj
Mixed and Mastered by Santhosh Narayanan at Future Tense Studios
Musicians Coordinator : Meenakshi Santhosh

Movie Credits:-
Written & Directed by: Mahi V Raghav
Producer: Shiva Meka
Banners: Three Autumn Leaves, V Celluloid
Music Director: Santhosh Narayanan
DOP : Madhie
Editor : Shravan Katikaneni
Art Director: Selva Kumar
Cast :
Mammootty, Jiiva, Ketaki Narayan, Suzanne Bernert, Mahesh Manjrekar

Lyrics:-
Pallavi:
Choodu Naannaa...Choosthunnaavaa naannaa.. Needa leni nena veella dheema
yemitii enthatiii premaa.. 
Naa dhareto thochakunte 
 Nii vembadae memu antuu
Kadilaaru ento aa nammakam
Nenelaa odduku  cheradam...  Veellanelaa  odduku cherchadam

Charanam 1:
Inti peddhaa.. Kanumoosthey ainavaallu anadhale kadha. 
Nuvvu lekaa.. Prathi ooruu ooruu anadha avvadam yendayyaa..
  Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa...
Idhi yenaaduu.. Jarigundadhayyaa.. Oo pedayya.. 
Indhari kannulu chimme kanniitinanthaa..
Thudavaalani vundhi kodukuga
Anduku avasaramaiyyee kondantha dhairyam naakivvu..

Charanam 2:
enthala abhimaaname kuripisthunnaro ee janam Anduke ee janmalo teerchesukuntaa ee runam Gadapaki prathi gadapaki nenavuthaa raksha thoranam  Maatapai untaanani chesthunnaa tholi santhakam
Needa leni nena veella dheema...
Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
     Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3984: Sher Ko Kara Repair
--------------------------------------------------------
Sodhi announces his plan to get his car repaired, prompting Roshan to playfully remind him of the troubles it caused. Jethalal suggests getting a new car, but Sodhi opts to repair the existing one. Later, Sodhi has to drop Roshan at her relative's place and Tapu asks him if he can drop Tapu Sena to the mall.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3984, 18 Jan 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: कैसे अपनी ज़िंदगी को बेहतर बनाएँ | Dr Vikas Divyakirti | Drishti IAS @vikasdivyakirti
snippet.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

अक्सर ही ऐसा होता है कि जिसे एक समय हम जीवन की सफलता मान बैठते हैं, समय के साथ वह केवल एक पड़ाव की तरह लगने लगता है। और सफलता हमें वह संतोष नहीं दे पाती है, जिसके अपेक्षा हम कर रहे होते हैं। इसलिये अपने जीवन में हमें 'सफलता' के साथ-साथ 'सार्थकता' की भी खोज करनी चाहिये। 

इस छोटी सी चर्चा में डॉ. विकास दिव्यकीर्ति सर द्वारा इसी द्वंद्व को समझाने की कोशिश की गई है। सांसारिक सफलताओं के साथ-साथ आत्मिक उन्नति को कैसे साधा जा सकता है, इसका सूत्र भी आपको इस चर्चा में मिलेगा। 

उम्मीद है इससे आपको अपनी ज़िंदगी बेहतर बनाने में मदद मिलेगी। 

शुभकामनाओं सहित, 
टीम दृष्टि

To follow on Instagram, visit https://www.instagram.com/divyakirti.vikas

localized.title: कैसे अपनी ज़िंदगी को बेहतर बनाएँ | Dr Vikas Divyakirti | Drishti IAS @vikasdivyakirti
localized.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

अक्सर ही ऐसा होता है कि जिसे एक समय हम जीवन की सफलता मान बैठते हैं, समय के साथ वह केवल एक पड़ाव की तरह लगने लगता है। और सफलता हमें वह संतोष नहीं दे पाती है, जिसके अपेक्षा हम कर रहे होते हैं। इसलिये अपने जीवन में हमें 'सफलता' के साथ-साथ 'सार्थकता' की भी खोज करनी चाहिये। 

इस छोटी सी चर्चा में डॉ. विकास दिव्यकीर्ति सर द्वारा इसी द्वंद्व को समझाने की कोशिश की गई है। सांसारिक सफलताओं के साथ-साथ आत्मिक उन्नति को कैसे साधा जा सकता है, इसका सूत्र भी आपको इस चर्चा में मिलेगा। 

उम्मीद है इससे आपको अपनी ज़िंदगी बेहतर बनाने में मदद मिलेगी। 

शुभकामनाओं सहित, 
टीम दृष्टि

snippet.title: Shri Ram Lalla | Sonu Nigam | Ram Bhajan | Amitabh S Verma | Mukul Varma | Ram Mandir Song
snippet.description:
Get ready to feel the joy! "Shri Ram Lalla" song in Sonu Nigam's voice is all about the happiness of Lord Ram coming back to #Ayodhya. This special song is like a musical hug for everyone excited for #RamMandir.

The beautiful city of #Ayodhya is getting ready for a big celebration, and this song captures that wonderful feeling.

Singer - Sonu Nigam 
Lyrics -   Mukul Varma  
               Amitabh S Verma

snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Sri Lanka vs Zimbabwe | Highlights | 16th January 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-zimbabwe-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700001364

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Zimbabwe won the toss and decided to bowl first in the 2nd T20I. Sri Lanka lost their top three batters for one-digit scores but later Charith Asalanka and Angelo Mathews stitched up a brilliant partnership. Sri Lanka ended with a total of 173 runs and Zimbabwe then came into bat. Opener Craig Ervine played a superb knock worth 70 runs while Luke Jongwe and Clive Madande's heroics ultimately took Zimbabwe to a thrilling four-wicket victory.

snippet.title: बाजरा की फूली फूली इडली-पोषण से भरपूर-सर्दियों के लिये खास नाश्ता-Nutrient-Rich Millet Idli Recipe
snippet.description:
बाजरे की न्यूट्रीएन्ट पैक्ड-ग्लूटन फ्री इडली, Healthy Bajra Idli Recipe, Wholesome Breakfast,Bajra Flour Recipes,Nutrient-packed Bajra Idli Recipe
#millet #bajrarecipe #winterspecial #idli 

𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐚𝐣𝐫𝐚 𝐈𝐝𝐥𝐢
बाजरा आटा - Pearl millet flour - 1 cup (140 grams)
सूजी - Semolina - 1/4 cup (50 grams)
दही - Curd - 3/4 cup
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
हरे मटर - Green peas - 1/2 cup
इनो फ्रुट सॉल्ट - Eno fruit salt - 1 tsp
 
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐂𝐡𝐮𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐲
मूंगफली - Peanuts - 1/2 cup
नारियल - Coconut - 1/2 cup, grated
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 2 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1 inch
नींबू का रस - Lemon juice - 2 tsp
तेल - Oil - 3 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1 tsp
उरद दाल - Urad dal - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 2 no
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves - 20-25 no

snippet.title: यह लोकतंत्र नहीं, धर्मतंत्र है
snippet.description:
लोकतंत्र की जगह धर्मतंत्र ने ली है। इस धर्मतंत्र के सामने भारत के लोकतंत्र की तस्वीर धुंधली होती जा रही है बल्कि धर्मतंत्र इतना हावी हो चुका है कि इसके बग़ैर आज के भारत में आप लोकतंत्र देख भी नहीं सकते हैं। धर्म तंत्र का मतलब ही ऐसा हो गया है कि पार्टियां धार्मिक आयोजन कराने वाली संस्था में बदलती जा रही हैं। पहले धर्म से दूरी बनाकर रखती थीं मगर अब पार्टियां राजनीति से ही दूरी बनाने लगी हैं। पूंजी के दबाव में राजनीतिक दलों के भीतर राजनीति खत्म हुई और अब धर्म का नाम लेकर लोकतंत्र के मैदान से ही राजनीतिक दल खत्म हो रहे हैं। अगर लोकतांत्रिक चरित्र पर धार्मिक चरित्र हावी हुआ तो वह लोकतंत्र को नौटंकी में बदल देगा। एक दिन धर्म भी नौटंकी की तरह नज़र आने लगेगा।मेरी इस बात को लिख कर पर्स में रख लीजिए

लोकतंत्र की जगह धर्मतंत्र ने ली है। इस धर्मतंत्र के सामने भारत के लोकतंत्र की तस्वीर धुंधली होती जा रही है बल्कि धर्मतंत्र इतना हावी हो चुका है कि इसके बग़ैर आज के भारत में आप लोकतंत्र देख भी नहीं सकते हैं। धर्म तंत्र का मतलब ही ऐसा हो गया है कि पार्टियां धार्मिक आयोजन कराने वाली संस्था में बदलती जा रही हैं। पहले धर्म से दूरी बनाकर रखती थीं मगर अब पार्टियां राजनीति से ही दूरी बनाने लगी हैं। पूंजी के दबाव में राजनीतिक दलों के भीतर राजनीति खत्म हुई और अब धर्म का नाम लेकर लोकतंत्र के मैदान से ही राजनीतिक दल खत्म हो रहे हैं। अगर लोकतांत्रिक चरित्र पर धार्मिक चरित्र हावी हुआ तो वह लोकतंत्र को नौटंकी में बदल देगा। एक दिन धर्म भी नौटंकी की तरह नज़र आने लगेगा।मेरी इस बात को लिख कर पर्स में रख लीजिए

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0yXUUIaPVAqZLgRjvtMftw/join

snippet.title: Coaching Centre: 16 साल से कम उम्र के बच्चों की Coaching बंद, आदेश नहीं मानने पर 1 लाख का जुर्माना
snippet.description:
Coaching Centre Banned For Students Under 16 Years: शिक्षा मंत्रालय द्वारा घोषित नए दिशानिर्देश के मुताबिक कोचिंग संस्थान 16 साल से कम उम्र के विद्यार्थियों को अपने यहां दाखिल नहीं कर सकेंगे और अच्छे नंबर या रैंक दिलाने की गारंटी जैसे भ्रामक वादे भी नहीं कर सकेंगे. कोचिंग संस्थानों को विनियमित करने के लिए दिशानिर्देश एक कानूनी ढांचे की आवश्यकता को पूरा करने और बेतरतीब तरीके से निजी कोचिंग संस्थानों की बढ़ोतरी को रोकने के लिए हैं. मंत्रालय ने यह दिशानिर्देश विद्यार्थियों की आत्महत्या के बढ़ते मामलों, आग की घटनाओं, कोचिंग संस्थानों में सुविधाओं की कमी के साथ-साथ उनके द्वारा अपनाई जाने वाली शिक्षण पद्धतियों के बारे में सरकार को मिली शिकायतों के बाद तैयार किए हैं.

snippet.title: Ayodhya Ram Mandir: 22 जनवरी से पहले कोई गड़बड़ मत करना... वरना योगी जी हैं ना ! Ground Report
snippet.description:
Ayodhya Ram Mandir: 22 जनवरी से पहले कोई गड़बड़ मत करना... वरना योगी जी हैं ना ! Ground Report
अयोध्या में प्राण प्रतिष्ठा में बस 8 दिन ही दिन बचे हैं...आज सीएम योगी भी अयोध्या पहुंचे ..तैयारियां देखीं...22 जनवरी को जब प्राण प्रतिष्ठा होगी...तो उस दिन अयोध्या में VIP'S का जमावड़ा होगा...ऐसे में कैसी है अयोध्या में सुरक्षा...कैसे योगी ने अयोध्या के चप्पे-चप्पे पर पहरेदारों को तैनात कर दिया है..दिखाते हैं आपको ये स्पेशल रिपोर्ट
